ctpp2 (2.8.3-6) unstable; urgency=low

  [ Vasudev Kamath ]
  * Update patch 1004 to properly skip iconv library.
    Closes: bug#705134. Thanks to pinotree for pointers.
  * Add patch 1005 to fix FTBFS on Hurd and kFreeBSD.
    Closes: bug#721367. Thanks to Aaron M. Ucko and Pino Toscano.
  * Add generic override for libc*-dev to d-devlibs call: API and
    package name vary across (notably non-Linux) platforms.
    Thanks to Pino Toscano and Aaron M. Ucko.

  [ Jonas Smedegaard ]
  * Reorder patches to apply in numerical order.
  * Unfuzz patches with shortening quilt options.

